    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/functools.html"
  not_derived_from:
    - "any proprietary source"
  notes:
    - "Wave 602 (_extra2326): numeric constants and fixed-size attribute checks."
    - "WRAPPER_ASSIGNMENTS has 6 elements in Python 3.14: __module__, __name__, __qualname__, __doc__, __annotate__, __type_params__."
    - "Note: __annotations__ was replaced by __annotate__ in Python 3.14; __type_params__ was added."
    - "WRAPPER_UPDATES has 1 element: __dict__."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-12."
  created_at: "2026-04-12"

